<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1506,1747]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,1018,1542,1567]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Recorded damage and economic importance in the orchards of Iran:</emphasis>
