<taxonomicName box="[1371,1436,1543,1566]" class="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" family="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" genus="Pyrus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mollusca (awaiting allocation)" pageId="12" pageNumber="487" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1371,1436,1543,1566]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Pyrus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. (
<bibRefCitation box="[197,337,1578,1603]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487" refId="ref21632" refString="Rajabi, Gh. (1991) Insects attacking Rosaceous fruit trees in Iran. Vol. 3: Homoptera. Ministry of Agriculture, Tehran, 256 pp." type="book">Rajabi 1991</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation box="[349,479,1578,1603]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487" refId="ref17343" refString="Abaii, M. (2000) Pests of Forest Trees and Shrubs of Iran. 2 nd Edition. Ministry of Agriculture, Agricultural Research, Education &amp; Extension Organization, Tehran, 178 pp." type="book">Abaii 2000</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1506,1747]" box="[199,1096,1614,1639]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,934,1614,1639]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Recorded damage in the orchards of other parts of the world:</emphasis>
Not recorded.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1506,1747]" box="[199,1035,1650,1675]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,562,1650,1675]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Recorded distribution in Iran:</emphasis>
Southwest (
<bibRefCitation box="[700,1023,1650,1675]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487" refId="ref20841" refString="Mozaffarian, F. &amp; Wilson, M. R. (2016) A checklist of the leafhoppers of Iran (Hemiptera: Auchenorrhyncha: Cicadellidae). Zootaxa, 4062 (1), 1 - 63. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4062.1.1" type="journal article">Mozaffarian &amp; Wilson 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,1506,1747]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,342,1686,1711]" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Conclusion:</emphasis>
The species is endemic to 
<collectingCountry box="[642,687,1687,1710]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Iran</collectingCountry>
and limited to 
<collectingRegion box="[856,904,1687,1710]" country="Iran" name="Fars" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Fars</collectingRegion>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[958,1076,1686,1711]" country="Iran" name="Khuzestan" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Khuzestan</collectingRegion>
provinces. Its pest status in 
<collectingCountry box="[1391,1436,1687,1710]" name="Iran" pageId="12" pageNumber="487">Iran</collectingCountry>
needs further confirmation.
</paragraph>
